{"tid":2426824,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我希望今日同聽日見到嘅係-星星之火也能燎原","createTime":"2021-02-28T10:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T11:43:46.000Z","uid":384104,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b905e12e6771a89b85d8c44f857c80e700c02b8e","tid":2426824,"uid":384104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:53:26.000Z","msg":"香港人反抗 從來都唔係一句口號<br />\n光復香港 時代革命更甚<br />\n而係一啲值得我地付上所有嘅精神同信念<br />\n<br />\n送一句說話比大家<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">這跟能不能嬴沒有關係 我都必須站在站在這裡抗爭到底<br />\n因為這就是我的責任</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2426557/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2426557/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n無論大家係咩派別 (港獨 本土定純黃絲)<br />\n同埋點睇議會戰線以至傳統老泛民 同同埋所謂嘅35+<br />\n<br />\n大家都要明白到一點<br />\n就係我地面對嘅敵人太強<br />\n只有我地互相團結起來 先有反抗嘅希望<br />\n<br />\n所以最初大家先會講<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong>兄弟爬山各自努力<br />\n不分化 不割席</strong></span><br />\n仲有依家大家都會講嘅匆鬥黃<br />\n<br />\n大概就係因為我地再冇呢個本錢<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">聽日西九要人<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"64c1322456efa23a75b196481a275dc0d5e62c99","tid":2426824,"uid":384104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d60851b9c499225d2c3be0fd1c2f896bb28bcd","tid":2426824,"uid":344609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc22666da3abe5bb7b7b24a956b3e05d4426180f","tid":2426824,"uid":344609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:56:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkg